3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with analyzing videos captured by low-cost cameras, which can be considered as multimedia data. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of neural networks for vehicle re-identification can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper briefly mentions false alarms caused by similar license plate strings, which can be considered as a security concern.
